<h2>Setting up for github pages</h2>

<pre><code>$ rake setup_github_pages
$ rake deploy
</code></pre>

<h2>Make a new post</h2>

<pre><code>$ rake new_post[title]
</code></pre>

<h2>Translate markdown to html file</h2>

<pre><code>$ rake generate
</code></pre>

<h2>Remove page</h2>

<pre><code>$ rm -rf [pages] 
$ rake generate 
$ rake deploy
</code></pre>

<h2>Read on Buttons in index page</h2>

<p>Check your _config.yml and find <em>excerpt_separator</em> <br>
default value is: <em>&lt;!&ndash;more&ndash;></em> <br>
add <strong>&lt;!&ndash;more&ndash;></strong> to the paragraph that you want to show in index page
<code>
excerpt_separator: "&lt;!--more--&gt;"
</code></p>

<p>e.g.
&#8220;`</p>

<h2>Installation</h2>

<p>$ git clone git://github.com/imathis/octopress.git
$ bundle install
$ rake install
$ rake preview</p>

<pre><code>---
## Install lucaslew/whitespace theme
</code></pre>

<p>$ cd octopress
$ git clone git://github.com/lucaslew/whitespace.git .themes/whitespace</p>

<h1>for zsh, use: rake install[&lsquo;whitespace&rsquo;]</h1>

<p>$ rake install[&lsquo;whitespace&rsquo;]
$ rake generate</p>

